Evidently a friend of a friend of a friend got invited. He IS drinking to excess and becoming a loud drunk. I explain politely to him that he needed to chill out or get out. He looks at me all glassy eyed and I figure thats that. Well he becomes a loud ass again but before I can get over to correct him, his girlfriend tries to quiet and calm him down. Well he didn't respond well to that and directs his focus and anger on her. <br />
<br />
Ok, Rule Number 1 in Baelan's World is : No violence against a woman. I've seen too much of it and I do not tolerate it. So I approach him and insert myself between he and his GF. Tell him he is leaving now. He calls me a name and takes a swing. considering I have a foot and 100 pounds on him...goes nowhere. So, I drag him out to the balcony to calm him down and allow a little perspective. Hanging him over the edge of a second floor balcony changes his attitude and he begins to find inner peace and sobriety.<br />
<br />
True story</div>
